# Sanity Rules

## Schema

- Define schemas in `schemas/` and co-locate GROQ queries with features.
- Name schema types in PascalCase (`Post`, `Author`).

## Queries

```ts
export const postBySlugQuery = groq`
  *[_type == "post" && slug.current == $slug][0]{
    title,
    body,
    author->{
      name,
      image
    }
  }
`;
```

## Client Usage

- Use `@sanity/client` inside server components or API routes only.
- Memoize the Sanity client; do not create a new client per request.

